    "body": "I don't think we should pursue this. The gas estimator cannot compare with an actual execution. For example, the rules for storage gas have become very complicated now, and the gas estimator computes this by \"statically\" looking at opcodes--we don't account for slots being warm or refunds. We should consider deprecating this.",
